{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Create a section with a customizable header at the top, followed by a split layout with left and right parts. The left side should display one main product with title, price, compare-at price, and add to cart button. The right side should display four smaller products in a grid, each with title, price, compare-at price, and add to cart button. Include extensive customization settings for all parameters: section header text and styling, background colors for header and sections, text colors, font sizes for all elements, padding and margins, section heights and widths, left and right section width ratios, button colors and styles, border options, spacing controls, and comprehensive visual parameters. Make it fully customizable with complete styling control and responsive design.

{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
